An 18-year-old Phelan, California girl was killed in a car crash with a dump truck just weeks after graduating from high school.

Nicole Lyle and 16-year-old Serrano High classmate John Cabrera were pronounced dead at the scene of the crash that injured three of their other friends in Cajon Pass late Tuesday.

Authorities have not officially identified the victims, but classmates named Lyle and Cabrera in posts on social media.Â 

